MOBSTER fit for the PD4120a breast sample.

PD4120a_breast_sample.Rd

MOBSTER fit for the PD4120a breast sample; this object is the result of running `mobster_fit` function on the input data described in the main MOBSTER paper.

data(PD4120a_breast_sample)

Format

Data from an example MOBSTER fit.

Examples

data(PD4120a_breast_sample, package = 'mobster')
print(PD4120a_breast_sample$best)
#> [ MOBSTER ] N = 4643 points with K = 3 Beta clusters, fit by MM in 259 steps [CONVERGED] 
#> 
#>   Components (fit)  
#>      Tail	n = 1006 (0.26) 	 Shape = 1.5 
#>   Beta C1 	n = 1740 (0.37) 	 Mean = 0.52
#>   Beta C2 	n = 1167 (0.24) 	 Mean = 0.29
#>   Beta C3 	n = 730 (0.13) 	 Mean = 0.16
#> 
#>   Scores (model selection)  
#>       NLL       BIC       AIC  entropy       ICL reduced.entropy     reICL size
#>  -3201.73 -6302.143 -6379.461 955.2519 -5346.891        188.3106 -6113.833   12
plot(PD4120a_breast_sample$best)
